title: Dante’s Inferno cantos XXIX and XXX
author: VD
content_html: We’re rapidly approaching the grand finale. Those Hellmarchers who have made it this far are to be commended… there’s no stopping now. Next week’s reading is cantos XXXI and XXXII.
